var book = {
	"name": "Hosea",
	"numChapters": 14,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Hosea, the son of Beeri, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22096A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22096A\"></sup>in the days of Uzziah, Jotham, Ahaz, and Hezekiah, kings of Judah, and in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22096B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22096B\"></sup>Jeroboam the son of Joash, king of Israel.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> first spoke through Hosea, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Hosea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22097C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22097C\"></sup>“Go, take to yourself a wife of whoredom and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22097D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22097D\"></sup>children of whoredom, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22097E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22097E\"></sup>the land commits great whoredom by forsaking the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So he went and took Gomer, the daughter of Diblaim, and she conceived and bore him a son.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to him, “Call his name Jezreel, for in just a little while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22099F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22099F\"></sup>I will punish the house of Jehu for the blood of Jezreel, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22099G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22099G\"></sup>I will put an end to the kingdom of the house of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And on that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22100H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22100H\"></sup>I will break the bow of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22100I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22100I\"></sup>in the Valley of Jezreel.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>She conceived again and bore a daughter. And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22101J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22101J\"></sup>“Call her name No Mercy, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22101K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22101K\"></sup>I will no more have mercy on the house of Israel, to forgive them at all.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22102L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22102L\"></sup>I will have mercy on the house of Judah, and I will save them by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God. I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22102M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22102M\"></sup>will not save them by bow or by sword or by war or by horses or by horsemen.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When she had weaned No Mercy, she conceived and bore a son.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22104N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22104N\"></sup>“Call his name Not My People, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22104O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22104O\"></sup>you are not my people, and I am not your God.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup> Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22105P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22105P\"></sup>the number of the children of Israel shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22105Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22105Q\"></sup>like the sand of the sea, which cannot be measured or numbered. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22105R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22105R\"></sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22105S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22105S\"></sup>in the place where it was said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22105T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22105T\"></sup>“You are not my people,” it shall be said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22105U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22105U\"></sup>“Children of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22105V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22105V\"></sup>the living God.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22106W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22106W\"></sup>the children of Judah and the children of Israel shall be gathered together, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22106X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22106X\"></sup>they shall appoint for themselves one head. And they shall go up from the land, for great shall be the day of Jezreel."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span> Say to your brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22107A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22107A\"></sup>“You are my people,” and to your sisters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22107B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22107B\"></sup>“You have received mercy.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Plead with your mother, plead—for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22108C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22108C\"></sup>she is not my wife,and I am not her husband—that she put away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22108D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22108D\"></sup>her whoring from her face,and her adultery from between her breasts;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>lest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22109E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22109E\"></sup>I strip her nakedand make her as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22109F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22109F\"></sup>in the day she was born,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22109G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22109G\"></sup>make her like a wilderness,and make her like a parched land,and kill her with thirst.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22110H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22110H\"></sup>Upon her children also I will have no mercy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22110I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22110I\"></sup>because they are children of whoredom.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22111J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22111J\"></sup>their mother has played the whore;she who conceived them has acted shamefully.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22111K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22111K\"></sup>she said, ‘I will go after my lovers,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22111L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22111L\"></sup>give me my bread and my water,my wool and my flax, my oil and my drink.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22112M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22112M\"></sup>I will hedge up her way with thorns,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22112N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22112N\"></sup>I will build a wall against her,so that she cannot find her paths.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>She shall pursue her loversbut not overtake them,and she shall seek thembut shall not find them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22113O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22113O\"></sup>Then she shall say,‘I will go and return to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22113P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22113P\"></sup>my first husband,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22113Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22113Q\"></sup>for it was better for me then than now.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22114R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22114R\"></sup>she did not knowthat it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22114S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22114S\"></sup>I who gave her<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22114T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22114T\"></sup>the grain, the wine, and the oil,and who lavished on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22114U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22114U\"></sup>her silver and gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22114V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22114V\"></sup>which they used for Baal.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22115W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22115W\"></sup>I will take backmy grain in its time,and my wine in its season,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22115X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22115X\"></sup>I will take away my wool and my flax,which were to cover her nakedness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22116Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22116Y\"></sup>I will uncover her lewdnessin the sight of her lovers,and no one shall rescue her out of my hand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22117Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22117Z\"></sup>And I will put an end to all her mirth,her feasts, her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22117AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22117AA\"></sup>new moons, her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22117AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22117AB\"></sup>Sabbaths,and all her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22117AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22117AC\"></sup>appointed feasts.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22118AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22118AD\"></sup>I will lay waste her vines and her fig trees,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22118AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22118AE\"></sup>of which she said,‘These are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22118AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22118AF\"></sup>my wages,which my lovers have given me.’I will make them a forest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22118AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22118AG\"></sup>and the beasts of the field shall devour them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22119AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22119AH\"></sup>I will punish her for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22119AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22119AI\"></sup>the feast days of the Baalswhen she burned offerings to themand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22119AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22119AJ\"></sup>adorned herself with her ring and jewelry,and went after her loversand forgot me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Therefore, behold, I will allure her,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22120AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22120AK\"></sup>bring her into the wilderness,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22120AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22120AL\"></sup>speak tenderly to her.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And there I will give her her vineyardsand make the Valley of Achor a door of hope.And there she shall answer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22121AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22121AM\"></sup>as in the days of her youth,as at the time when she came out of the land of Egypt.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22122AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22122AN\"></sup>in that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you will call me ‘My Husband,’ and no longer will you call me ‘My Baal.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22123AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22123AO\"></sup>I will remove the names of the Baals from her mouth, and they shall be remembered by name no more.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22124AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22124AP\"></sup>I will make for them a covenant on that day with the beasts of the field, the birds of the heavens, and the creeping things of the ground. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22124AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22124AQ\"></sup>I will abolish the bow, the sword, and war from the land, and I will make you lie down in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22124AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22124AR\"></sup>safety.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I will betroth you to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22125AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22125AS\"></sup>forever. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22125AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22125AT\"></sup>I will betroth you to me in righteousness and in justice, in steadfast love and in mercy.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22126AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22126AU\"></sup>I will betroth you to me in faithfulness. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22126AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22126AV\"></sup>you shall know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22127AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22127AW\"></sup>in that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22127AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22127AX\"></sup>I will answer, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,I will answer the heavens,and they shall answer the earth,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and the earth shall answer the grain, the wine, and the oil,and they shall answer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22128AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22128AY\"></sup>Jezreel,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22129AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22129AZ\"></sup>I will sow her for myself in the land.And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22129BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22129BA\"></sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22129BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22129BB\"></sup>will have mercy on No Mercy,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22129BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22129BC\"></sup>I will say to Not My People, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22129BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22129BD\"></sup>‘You are my people’;and he shall say, ‘You are my God.’”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22130A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22130A\"></sup>“Go again, love a woman who is loved by another man and is an adulteress, even as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loves the children of Israel, though they turn to other gods and love cakes of raisins.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I bought her for fifteen shekels of silver and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22131B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22131B\"></sup>homer and a lethech of barley.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I said to her, “You must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22132C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22132C\"></sup>dwell as mine for many days. You shall not play the whore, or belong to another man; so will I also be to you.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the children of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22133D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22133D\"></sup>shall dwell many days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22133E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22133E\"></sup>without king or prince, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22133F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22133F\"></sup>without sacrifice or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22133G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22133G\"></sup>pillar, without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22133H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22133H\"></sup>ephod or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22133I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22133I\"></sup>household gods.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Afterward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22134J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22134J\"></sup>the children of Israel shall return and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22134K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22134K\"></sup>seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22134L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22134L\"></sup>David their king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22134M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22134M\"></sup>and they shall come in fear to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and to his goodness in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22134N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22134N\"></sup>latter days."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22135A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22135A\"></sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O children of Israel,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22135B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22135B\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a controversy with the inhabitants of the land.There is no faithfulness or steadfast love,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22135C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22135C\"></sup>no knowledge of God in the land;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22136D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22136D\"></sup>there is swearing, lying, murder, stealing, and committing adultery;they break all bounds, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22136E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22136E\"></sup>bloodshed follows bloodshed.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22137F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22137F\"></sup>the land mourns,and all who dwell in it languish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22137G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22137G\"></sup>and also the beasts of the fieldand the birds of the heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22137H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22137H\"></sup>and even the fish of the sea are taken away.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22138I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22138I\"></sup>Yet let no one contend,and let none accuse,for with you is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22138J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22138J\"></sup>my contention, O priest.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You shall stumble by day;the prophet also shall stumble with you by night;and I will destroy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22139K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22139K\"></sup>your mother.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>My people are destroyed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22140L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22140L\"></sup>for lack of knowledge;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22140M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22140M\"></sup>because you have rejected knowledge,I reject you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22140N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22140N\"></sup>from being a priest to me.And since you have forgotten the law of your God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22140O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22140O\"></sup>I also will forget your children.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22141P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22141P\"></sup>The more they increased,the more they sinned against me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22141Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22141Q\"></sup>I will change their glory into shame.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22142R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22142R\"></sup>They feed on the sin of my people;they are greedy for their iniquity.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22143S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22143S\"></sup>And it shall be like people, like priest;I will punish them for their waysand repay them for their deeds.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22144T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22144T\"></sup>They shall eat, but not be satisfied;they shall play the whore, but not multiply,because they have forsaken the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>to cherish",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">11 </sup>whoredom, wine, and new wine,which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22145U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22145U\"></sup>take away the understanding.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>My people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22146V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22146V\"></sup>inquire of a piece of wood,and their walking staff gives them oracles.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22146W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22146W\"></sup>a spirit of whoredom has led them astray,and they have left their God to play the whore.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22147X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22147X\"></sup>They sacrifice on the tops of the mountainsand burn offerings on the hills,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22147Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22147Y\"></sup>under oak, poplar, and terebinth,because their shade is good.Therefore your daughters play the whore,and your brides commit adultery.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will not punish your daughters when they play the whore,nor your brides when they commit adultery;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22148Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22148Z\"></sup>the men themselves go aside with prostitutesand sacrifice with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22148AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22148AA\"></sup>cult prostitutes,and a people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22148AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22148AB\"></sup>without understanding shall come to ruin.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Though you play the whore, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22149AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22149AC\"></sup>Israel,let not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22149AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22149AD\"></sup>Judah become guilty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22149AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22149AE\"></sup>Enter not into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22149AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22149AF\"></sup>Gilgal,nor go up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22149AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22149AG\"></sup>Beth-aven,and swear not, “As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Like a stubborn heifer,Israel is stubborn;can the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> now feed themlike a lamb in a broad pasture?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22151AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22151AH\"></sup>Ephraim is joined to idols;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22151AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22151AI\"></sup>leave him alone.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When their drink is gone, they give themselves to whoring;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22152AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22152AJ\"></sup>their rulers dearly love shame.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22153AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22153AK\"></sup>A wind has wrapped them in its wings,and they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22153AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22153AL\"></sup>be ashamed because of their sacrifices."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22154A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22154A\"></sup>Hear this, O priests!Pay attention, O house of Israel!Give ear, O house of the king!For the judgment is for you;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22154B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22154B\"></sup>you have been a snare at Mizpahand a net spread upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22154C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22154C\"></sup>Tabor.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22155D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22155D\"></sup>the revolters <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22155E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22155E\"></sup>have gone deep into slaughter,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22155F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22155F\"></sup>I will discipline all of them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22156G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22156G\"></sup>I know Ephraim,and Israel is not hidden from me;for now, O Ephraim, you have played the whore;Israel is defiled.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22157H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22157H\"></sup>Their deeds do not permit themto return to their God.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22157I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22157I\"></sup>the spirit of whoredom is within them,and they know not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22158J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22158J\"></sup>The pride of Israel testifies to his face;Israel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22158K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22158K\"></sup>Ephraim shall stumble in his guilt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22158L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22158L\"></sup>Judah also shall stumble with them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22159M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22159M\"></sup>With their flocks and herds they shall goto seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22159N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22159N\"></sup>but they will not find him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22159O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22159O\"></sup>he has withdrawn from them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22160P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22160P\"></sup>They have dealt faithlessly with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;for they have borne alien children.Now the new moon shall devour them with their fields.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22161Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22161Q\"></sup>Blow the horn in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22161R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22161R\"></sup>Gibeah,the trumpet in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22161S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22161S\"></sup>Ramah.Sound the alarm at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22161T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22161T\"></sup>Beth-aven;we follow you, O Benjamin!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Ephraim shall become a desolationin the day of punishment;among the tribes of IsraelI make known what is sure.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The princes of Judah have becomelike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22163U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22163U\"></sup>those who move the landmark;upon them I will pour outmy wrath like water.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22164V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22164V\"></sup>oppressed, crushed in judgment,because he was determined to go after filth.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22165W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22165W\"></sup>like a moth to Ephraim,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22165X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22165X\"></sup>like dry rot to the house of Judah.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When Ephraim saw his sickness,and Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22166Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22166Y\"></sup>his wound,then Ephraim went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22166Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22166Z\"></sup>to Assyria,and sent to the great king.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22166AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22166AA\"></sup>But he is not able to cure youor heal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22166AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22166AB\"></sup>your wound.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For I will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22167AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22167AC\"></sup>like a lion to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22167AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22167AD\"></sup>Ephraim,and like a young lion to the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22167AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22167AE\"></sup>Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22167AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22167AF\"></sup>I, even I, will tear and go away;I will carry off, and no one shall rescue.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22168AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22168AG\"></sup>I will return again to my place,until they acknowledge their guilt and seek my face,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22168AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22168AH\"></sup>in their distress earnestly seek me."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“Come, let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22169A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22169A\"></sup>return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22169B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22169B\"></sup>he has torn us, that he may heal us;he has struck us down, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22169C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22169C\"></sup>he will bind us up.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>After two days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22170D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22170D\"></sup>he will revive us;on the third day he will raise us up,that we may live before him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22171E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22171E\"></sup>Let us know; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22171F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22171F\"></sup>let us press on to know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22171G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22171G\"></sup>his going out is sure as the dawn;he will come to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22171H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22171H\"></sup>as the showers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22171I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22171I\"></sup>as the spring rains that water the earth.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>What shall I do with you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22172J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22172J\"></sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22172K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22172K\"></sup>Ephraim?What shall I do with you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22172L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22172L\"></sup>Judah?Your love is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22172M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22172M\"></sup>like a morning cloud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22172N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22172N\"></sup>like the dew that goes early away.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore I have hewn them by the prophets;I have slain them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22173O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22173O\"></sup>by the words of my mouth,and my judgment goes forth as the light.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22174P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22174P\"></sup>I desire steadfast love and not sacrifice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22174Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22174Q\"></sup>the knowledge of God rather than burnt offerings.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22175R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22175R\"></sup>like Adam they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22175S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22175S\"></sup>transgressed the covenant;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22175T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22175T\"></sup>there they dealt faithlessly with me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22176U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22176U\"></sup>Gilead is a city of evildoers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22176V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22176V\"></sup>tracked with blood.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As robbers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22177W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22177W\"></sup>lie in wait for a man,so the priests band together;they murder on the way to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22177X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22177X\"></sup>Shechem;they commit villainy.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In the house of Israel I have seen a horrible thing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22178Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22178Y\"></sup>Ephraim's whoredom is there; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22178Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22178Z\"></sup>Israel is defiled.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For you also, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22179AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22179AA\"></sup>Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22179AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22179AB\"></sup>a harvest is appointed.When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22179AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22179AC\"></sup>I restore the fortunes of my people,"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22180A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22180A\"></sup>when I would heal Israel,the iniquity of Ephraim is revealed,and the evil deeds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22180B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22180B\"></sup>Samaria,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22180C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22180C\"></sup>they deal falsely;the thief breaks in,and the bandits raid outside.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But they do not considerthat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22181D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22181D\"></sup>I remember all their evil.Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22181E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22181E\"></sup>their deeds surround them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22181F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22181F\"></sup>they are before my face.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>By their evil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22182G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22182G\"></sup>they make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22182H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22182H\"></sup>the king glad,and the princes by their treachery.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22183I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22183I\"></sup>They are all adulterers;they are like a heated ovenwhose baker ceases to stir the fire,from the kneading of the doughuntil it is leavened.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On the day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22184J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22184J\"></sup>our king, the princesbecame sick with the heat of wine;he stretched out his hand with mockers.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For with hearts like an oven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22185K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22185K\"></sup>they approach their intrigue;all night their anger smolders;in the morning it blazes like a flaming fire.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All of them are hot as an oven,and they devour their rulers.All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22186L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22186L\"></sup>their kings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22186M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22186M\"></sup>have fallen,and none of them calls upon me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Ephraim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22187N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22187N\"></sup>mixes himself with the peoples;Ephraim is a cake not turned.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22188O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22188O\"></sup>Strangers devour his strength,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22188P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22188P\"></sup>he knows it not;gray hairs are sprinkled upon him,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22188Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22188Q\"></sup>he knows it not.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22189R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22189R\"></sup>The pride of Israel testifies to his face;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22189S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22189S\"></sup>yet they do not return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God,nor seek him, for all this.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim is like a dove,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22190T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22190T\"></sup>silly and without sense,calling to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22190U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22190U\"></sup>Egypt, going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22190V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22190V\"></sup>Assyria.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As they go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22191W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22191W\"></sup>I will spread over them my net;I will bring them down like birds of the heavens;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22191X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22191X\"></sup>I will discipline them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22191Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22191Y\"></sup>according to the report made to their congregation.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22192Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22192Z\"></sup>Woe to them, for they have strayed from me!Destruction to them, for they have rebelled against me!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22192AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22192AA\"></sup>I would redeem them,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22192AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22192AB\"></sup>they speak lies against me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22193AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22193AC\"></sup>They do not cry to me from the heart,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22193AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22193AD\"></sup>they wail upon their beds;for grain and wine they gash themselves;they rebel against me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Although <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22194AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22194AE\"></sup>I trained and strengthened their arms,yet they devise evil against me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22195AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22195AF\"></sup>return, but not upward;they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22195AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22195AG\"></sup>like a treacherous bow;their princes shall fall by the swordbecause of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22195AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22195AH\"></sup>the insolence of their tongue.This shall be their derision <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22195AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22195AI\"></sup>in the land of Egypt."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22196A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22196A\"></sup>the trumpet to your lips!One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22196B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22196B\"></sup>like a vulture is over the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22196C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22196C\"></sup>they have transgressed my covenantand rebelled against my law.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To me they cry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22197D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22197D\"></sup>“My God, we—Israel—know you.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Israel has spurned the good;the enemy shall pursue him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22199E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22199E\"></sup>They made kings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22199F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22199F\"></sup>but not through me.They set up princes, but I knew it not.With their silver and gold they made idolsfor their own destruction.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22200G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22200G\"></sup>I have spurned your calf, O Samaria.My anger burns against them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22200H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22200H\"></sup>How long will they be incapable of innocence?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For it is from Israel;a craftsman made it;it is not God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22201I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22201I\"></sup>The calf of Samaria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22201J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22201J\"></sup>shall be broken to pieces.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22202K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22202K\"></sup>they sow the wind,and they shall reap the whirlwind.The standing grain has no heads;it shall yield no flour;if it were to yield,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22202L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22202L\"></sup>strangers would devour it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22203M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22203M\"></sup>Israel is swallowed up;already they are among the nationsas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22203N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22203N\"></sup>a useless vessel.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22204O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22204O\"></sup>they have gone up to Assyria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22204P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22204P\"></sup>a wild donkey wandering alone;Ephraim has hired lovers.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Though they hire allies among the nations,I will soon gather them up.And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22205Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22205Q\"></sup>the king and princes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22205R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22205R\"></sup>shall soon writhebecause of the tribute.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Because Ephraim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22206S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22206S\"></sup>has multiplied altars for sinning,they have become to him altars for sinning.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22207T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22207T\"></sup>Were I to write for him my laws by the ten thousands,they would be regarded as a strange thing.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>As for my sacrificial offerings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22208U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22208U\"></sup>they sacrifice meat and eat it,but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not accept them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22208V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22208V\"></sup>Now he will remember their iniquityand punish their sins;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22208W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22208W\"></sup>they shall return to Egypt.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22209X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22209X\"></sup>Israel has forgotten <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22209Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22209Y\"></sup>his Makerand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22209Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22209Z\"></sup>built palaces,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22209AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22209AA\"></sup>Judah has multiplied fortified cities;so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22209AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22209AB\"></sup>I will send a fire upon his cities,and it shall devour her strongholds."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Rejoice not, O Israel!Exult not like the peoples;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22210A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22210A\"></sup>for you have played the whore, forsaking your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22210B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22210B\"></sup>You have loved a prostitute's wageson all threshing floors.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22211C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22211C\"></sup>Threshing floor and wine vat shall not feed them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22211D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22211D\"></sup>the new wine shall fail them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They shall not remain in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22212E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22212E\"></sup>the land of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22212F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22212F\"></sup>Ephraim shall return to Egypt,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22212G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22212G\"></sup>they shall eat unclean food in Assyria.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22213H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22213H\"></sup>They shall not pour drink offerings of wine to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22213I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22213I\"></sup>and their sacrifices shall not please him.It shall be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22213J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22213J\"></sup>mourners' bread to them;all who eat of it shall be defiled;for their bread shall be for their hunger only;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22213K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22213K\"></sup>it shall not come to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22214L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22214L\"></sup>What will you do on the day of the appointed festival,and on the day of the feast of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For behold, they are going away from destruction;but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22215M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22215M\"></sup>Egypt shall gather them;Memphis shall bury them.Nettles shall possess <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22215N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22215N\"></sup>their precious things of silver;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22215O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22215O\"></sup>thorns shall be in their tents.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22216P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22216P\"></sup>The days of punishment have come;the days of recompense have come;Israel shall know it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22216Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22216Q\"></sup>The prophet is a fool;the man of the spirit is mad,because of your great iniquityand great hatred.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The prophet is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22217R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22217R\"></sup>the watchman of Ephraim with my God;yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22217S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22217S\"></sup>a fowler's snare is on all his ways,and hatred in the house of his God.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22218T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22218T\"></sup>They have deeply corrupted themselvesas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22218U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22218U\"></sup>in the days of Gibeah:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22218V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22218V\"></sup>he will remember their iniquity;he will punish their sins.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Like grapes in the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22219W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22219W\"></sup>I found Israel.Like the first fruit on the fig treein its first season,I saw your fathers.But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22219X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22219X\"></sup>they came to Baal-peorand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22219Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22219Y\"></sup>consecrated themselves to the thing of shame,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22219Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22219Z\"></sup>became detestable like the thing they loved.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22220AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22220AA\"></sup>glory shall fly away like a bird—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22220AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22220AB\"></sup>no birth, no pregnancy, no conception!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22221AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22221AC\"></sup>Even if they bring up children,I will bereave them till none is left.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22221AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22221AD\"></sup>Woe to themwhen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22221AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22221AE\"></sup>I depart from them!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Ephraim, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22222AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22222AF\"></sup>as I have seen, was like a young palm planted in a meadow;but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22222AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22222AG\"></sup>Ephraim must lead his children out to slaughter.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Give them, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—what will you give?Give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22223AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22223AH\"></sup>a miscarrying womband dry breasts.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Every evil of theirs is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22224AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22224AI\"></sup>Gilgal;there I began to hate them.Because of the wickedness of their deedsI will drive them out of my house.I will love them no more;all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22224AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22224AJ\"></sup>their princes are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22224AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22224AK\"></sup>rebels.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Ephraim is stricken;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22225AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22225AL\"></sup>their root is dried up;they shall bear no fruit.Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22225AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22225AM\"></sup>though they give birth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22225AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22225AN\"></sup>I will put their beloved children to death.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22226AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22226AO\"></sup>My God will reject thembecause they have not listened to him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22226AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22226AP\"></sup>they shall be wanderers among the nations."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22227A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22227A\"></sup>Israel is a luxuriant vinethat yields its fruit.The more his fruit increased,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22227B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22227B\"></sup>the more altars he built;as his country improved,he improved his pillars.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Their heart is false;now they must bear their guilt.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will break down their altarsand destroy their pillars.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For now they will say:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22229C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22229C\"></sup>“We have no king,for we do not fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;and a king—what could he do for us?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They utter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22230D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22230D\"></sup>mere words;with empty oaths they make covenants;so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22230E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22230E\"></sup>judgment springs up like poisonous weeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22230F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22230F\"></sup>in the furrows of the field.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The inhabitants of Samaria tremblefor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22231G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22231G\"></sup>the calf of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22231H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22231H\"></sup>Beth-aven.Its people mourn for it, and so do its idolatrous priests—those who rejoiced over it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22231I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22231I\"></sup>over its glory—for it has departed from them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22232J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22232J\"></sup>The thing itself shall be carried to Assyriaas tribute to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22232K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22232K\"></sup>the great king.Ephraim shall be put to shame,and Israel shall be ashamed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22232L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22232L\"></sup>of his idol.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22233M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22233M\"></sup>Samaria's king shall perishlike a twig on the face of the waters.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The high places of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22234N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22234N\"></sup>Aven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22234O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22234O\"></sup>the sin of Israel,shall be destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22234P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22234P\"></sup>Thorn and thistle shall grow upon their altars,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22234Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22234Q\"></sup>they shall say to the mountains, “Cover us,”and to the hills, “Fall on us.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22235R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22235R\"></sup>the days of Gibeah, you have sinned, O Israel;there they have continued.Shall not the war against the unjust overtake them in Gibeah?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22236S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22236S\"></sup>When I please, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22236T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22236T\"></sup>I will discipline them,and nations shall be gathered against themwhen they are bound up for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22236U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22236U\"></sup>their double iniquity.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim was a trained calfthat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22237V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22237V\"></sup>loved to thresh,and I spared her fair neck;but I will put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22237W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22237W\"></sup>Ephraim to the yoke;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22237X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22237X\"></sup>Judah must plow;Jacob must harrow for himself.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22238Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22238Y\"></sup>Sow for yourselves righteousness;reap steadfast love;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22238Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22238Z\"></sup>break up your fallow ground,for it is the time to seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,that he may come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22238AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22238AA\"></sup>rain righteousness upon you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22239AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22239AB\"></sup>You have plowed iniquity;you have reaped injustice;you have eaten the fruit of lies.Because you have trusted in your own wayand in the multitude of your warriors,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22240AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22240AC\"></sup>the tumult of war shall arise among your people,and all your fortresses shall be destroyed,as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22240AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22240AD\"></sup>Shalman destroyed Beth-arbel on the day of battle;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22240AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22240AE\"></sup>mothers were dashed in pieces with their children.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus it shall be done to you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22241AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22241AF\"></sup>Bethel,because of your great evil.At dawn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22241AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22241AG\"></sup>the king of Israelshall be utterly cut off."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22242A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22242A\"></sup>When Israel was a child, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22242B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22242B\"></sup>I loved him,and out of Egypt I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22242C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22242C\"></sup>called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22242D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22242D\"></sup>my son.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22243E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22243E\"></sup>The more they were called,the more they went away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22243F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22243F\"></sup>they kept sacrificing to the Baalsand burning offerings to idols.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Yet it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22244G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22244G\"></sup>I who taught Ephraim to walk;I took them up by their arms,but they did not know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22244H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22244H\"></sup>I healed them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22245I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22245I\"></sup>I led them with cords of kindness,with the bands of love,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22245J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22245J\"></sup>I became to them as one who eases the yoke on their jaws,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22245K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22245K\"></sup>I bent down to them and fed them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22246L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22246L\"></sup>They shall not return to the land of Egypt,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22246M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22246M\"></sup>Assyria shall be their king,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22246N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22246N\"></sup>because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22246O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22246O\"></sup>they have refused to return to me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22247P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22247P\"></sup>The sword shall rage against their cities,consume the bars of their gates,and devour them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22247Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22247Q\"></sup>because of their own counsels.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>My people are bent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22248R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22248R\"></sup>on turning away from me,and though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22248S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22248S\"></sup>they call out to the Most High,he shall not raise them up at all.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>How can I give you up, O Ephraim?How can I hand you over, O Israel?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22249T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22249T\"></sup>How can I make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22249U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22249U\"></sup>like Admah?How can I treat you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22249V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22249V\"></sup>like Zeboiim?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22249W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22249W\"></sup>My heart recoils within me;my compassion grows warm and tender.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will not execute my burning anger;I will not again destroy Ephraim;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22250X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22250X\"></sup>for I am God and not a man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22250Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22250Y\"></sup>the Holy One in your midst,and I will not come in wrath.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22251Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22251Z\"></sup>They shall go after the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22251AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22251AA\"></sup>he will roar like a lion;when he roars,his children shall come trembling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22251AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22251AB\"></sup>from the west;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>they shall come trembling like birds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22252AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22252AC\"></sup>from Egypt,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22252AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22252AD\"></sup>like doves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22252AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22252AE\"></sup>from the land of Assyria,and I will return them to their homes, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup> Ephraim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22253AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22253AF\"></sup>has surrounded me with lies,and the house of Israel with deceit,but Judah still walks with Godand is faithful to the Holy One."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Ephraim feeds on the windand pursues <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22254A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22254A\"></sup>the east wind all day long;they multiply <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22254B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22254B\"></sup>falsehood and violence;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22254C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22254C\"></sup>they make a covenant with Assyria,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22254D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22254D\"></sup>oil is carried to Egypt.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22255E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22255E\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has an indictment against Judahand will punish Jacob according to his ways;he will repay him according to his deeds.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22256F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22256F\"></sup>In the womb he took his brother by the heel,and in his manhood he strove with God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He strove with the angel and prevailed;he wept and sought his favor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22257G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22257G\"></sup>He met God at Bethel,and there God spoke with us—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22258H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22258H\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his memorial name:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“So you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22259I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22259I\"></sup>by the help of your God, return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22259J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22259J\"></sup>hold fast to love and justice,and wait continually for your God.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A merchant, in whose hands are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22260K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22260K\"></sup>false balances,he loves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22260L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22260L\"></sup>to oppress.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Ephraim has said, “Ah, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22261M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22261M\"></sup>I am rich;I have found wealth for myself;in all my labors <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22261N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22261N\"></sup>they cannot find in me iniquity or sin.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22262O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22262O\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godfrom the land of Egypt;I will again make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22262P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22262P\"></sup>dwell in tents,as in the days of the appointed feast.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22263Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22263Q\"></sup>I spoke to the prophets;it was I who multiplied <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22263R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22263R\"></sup>visions,and through the prophets gave parables.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22264S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22264S\"></sup>If there is iniquity in Gilead,they shall surely come to nothing:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22264T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22264T\"></sup>in Gilgal they sacrifice bulls;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22264U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22264U\"></sup>their altars also are like stone heaps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22264V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22264V\"></sup>on the furrows of the field.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22265W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22265W\"></sup>Jacob fled to the land of Aram;there Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22265X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22265X\"></sup>served for a wife,and for a wife he guarded sheep.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22266Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22266Y\"></sup>a prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22266Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22266Z\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> brought Israel up from Egypt,and by a prophet he was guarded.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22267AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22267AA\"></sup>Ephraim has given bitter provocation;so his Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22267AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22267AB\"></sup>will leave his bloodguilt on him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22267AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22267AC\"></sup>and will repay him for his disgraceful deeds."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>When Ephraim spoke, there was trembling;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22268A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22268A\"></sup>he was exalted in Israel,but he incurred guilt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22268B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22268B\"></sup>through Baal and died.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And now they sin more and more,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22269C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22269C\"></sup>make for themselves metal images,idols skillfully made of their silver,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22269D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22269D\"></sup>all of them the work of craftsmen.It is said of them,“Those who offer human sacrifice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22269E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22269E\"></sup>kiss calves!”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore they shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22270F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22270F\"></sup>like the morning mistor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22270G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22270G\"></sup>like the dew that goes early away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22270H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22270H\"></sup>like the chaff that swirls from the threshing flooror <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22270I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22270I\"></sup>like smoke from a window.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22271J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22271J\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godfrom the land of Egypt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22271K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22271K\"></sup>you know no God but me,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22271L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22271L\"></sup>besides me there is no savior.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22272M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22272M\"></sup>It was I who knew you in the wilderness,in the land of drought;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22273N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22273N\"></sup>but when they had grazed, they became full,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22273O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22273O\"></sup>they were filled, and their heart was lifted up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22273P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22273P\"></sup>therefore they forgot me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22274Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22274Q\"></sup>I am to them like a lion;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22274R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22274R\"></sup>like a leopard I will lurk beside the way.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will fall upon them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22275S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22275S\"></sup>like a bear robbed of her cubs;I will tear open their breast,and there I will devour them like a lion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22275T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22275T\"></sup>as a wild beast would rip them open.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He destroys you, O Israel,for you are against me, against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22276U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22276U\"></sup>your helper.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22277V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22277V\"></sup>Where now is your king, to save you in all your cities?Where are all your rulers—those of whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22277W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22277W\"></sup>you said,“Give me a king and princes”?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22278X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22278X\"></sup>I gave you a king in my anger,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22278Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22278Y\"></sup>I took him away in my wrath.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The iniquity of Ephraim is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22279Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22279Z\"></sup>bound up;his sin is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22279AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22279AA\"></sup>kept in store.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22280AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22280AB\"></sup>The pangs of childbirth come for him,but he is an unwise son,for at the right time he does not present himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22280AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22280AC\"></sup>at the opening of the womb.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22281AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22281AD\"></sup>I shall ransom them from the power of Sheol;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22281AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22281AE\"></sup>I shall redeem them from Death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22281AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22281AF\"></sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22281AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22281AG\"></sup>Death, where are your plagues?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22281AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22281AH\"></sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22281AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22281AI\"></sup>Sheol, where is your sting?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22281AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22281AJ\"></sup>Compassion is hidden from my eyes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22282AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22282AK\"></sup>he may flourish among his brothers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22282AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22282AL\"></sup>the east wind, the wind of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, shall come,rising from the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22282AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22282AM\"></sup>and his fountain shall dry up;his spring shall be parched;it shall strip <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22282AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22282AN\"></sup>his treasuryof every precious thing.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup> Samaria <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22283AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22283AO\"></sup>shall bear her guilt,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22283AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22283AP\"></sup>she has rebelled against her God;they shall fall by the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22283AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22283AQ\"></sup>their little ones shall be dashed in pieces,and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22283AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22283AR\"></sup>pregnant women ripped open."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22284A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22284A\"></sup>Return, O Israel, to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22284B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22284B\"></sup>you have stumbled because of your iniquity.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Take with you wordsand return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;say to him,“Take away all iniquity;accept <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22285C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22285C\"></sup>what is good,and we will pay with bulls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22285D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22285D\"></sup>the vows of our lips.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22286E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22286E\"></sup>Assyria shall not save us;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22286F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22286F\"></sup>we will not ride on horses;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22286G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22286G\"></sup>we will say no more, ‘Our God,’to the work of our hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22286H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22286H\"></sup>In you the orphan finds mercy.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22287I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22287I\"></sup>will heal their apostasy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22287J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22287J\"></sup>I will love them freely,for my anger has turned from them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22288K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22288K\"></sup>I will be like the dew to Israel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22288L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22288L\"></sup>he shall blossom like the lily;he shall take root like the trees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22288M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22288M\"></sup>of Lebanon;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>his shoots shall spread out;his beauty shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22289N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22289N\"></sup>like the olive,and his fragrance like Lebanon.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They shall return and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22290O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22290O\"></sup>dwell beneath my shadow;they shall flourish like the grain;they shall blossom like the vine;their fame shall be like the wine of Lebanon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22291P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22291P\"></sup>Ephraim, what have I to do with idols?It is I who answer and look after you.I am like an evergreen cypress;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22291Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22291Q\"></sup>from me comes your fruit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22292R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22292R\"></sup>Whoever is wise, let him understand these things;whoever is discerning, let him know them;for the ways of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are right,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22292S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22292S\"></sup>the upright walk in them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-22292T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-22292T\"></sup>but transgressors stumble in them."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;